<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.8">
<l>vārāru miḷaṅkoṅkai maitiliyai maṇampuṇarvāṉ</l>
<l>kārārtiṇ cilaiyiṟutta taṉikkāḷai karutumiṭam</l>
<l>ērārum peruñcelvat teḻilmaṟaiyōr nāṅkaitaṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>cīrārum malarpoḻilcūḻ tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where is manifest the unique youth who broke</l>
<l rend="indent">the sturdy, dark bow,</l>
<l>The one who embraced in marriage Maitili</l>
<l rend="indent">with bodice-covered young breasts,</l>
<l>Is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai in Nāṅkai, encircled by beautiful flower gardens,</l>
<l>With Vedic experts, the beauty of whose great [wealth of] learning</l>
<l rend="indent">is full of goodness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
